## üìå About the Project
The **Mood Movie Recommender** is a web application where users can select a mood (e.g., _happy, sad, bored, romantic_) and instantly receive a curated list of movies matching that mood.

It includes:
- Flask backend  
- MySQL database (Flask-SQLAlchemy + PyMySQL)  
- Tailwind-styled UI and dashboard  
- TMDb poster auto-fetch optional (see below)

